irements service subscription data security restrictions the campus card system is a closed proprietary system that runs on its own hardware and software to learn more see maintenance and protection of campus card electronic records on the security and confidentiality web page support to report malfunctioning card readers or cash to card machines submit a helpsu request or call 650 725 help 5 4357 after hours and holiday trouble calls are answered around the clock by university operators who refer system wide problems to on call repair technicians immediately individual user problems are processed at the start of the next business day rates for costs and monthly rates associated with setting up access readers data services activations and terminations see the campus card services rates page getting started to learn more about building access services or to order access readers submit a helpsu request last modified fri 18 nov 2011 at 17 21 pages about this service overview adding a device reader find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages id cards campus card services footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
